Developments have taken place in football since it was first discovered, some new equipments are added to this sport while others are eliminated.
Majority have always wondered why footballers puts on a vest that resembles felmale bras during football matches and even training session.

In female, majority have always assumed it is used for breast support although this is one assumption that we should take out of our brains.
This football vest or bra servers a similar fuction in both male and female athletes.
In this article I want enlighten you on why athletes or many sports organizations have embraced this vest and encourages players to used.
It is therefore even wrong to call it a bra because in the real sense it is not a bra. This vest is called the GPS vest.
From the above name one can easily ralate it’s fuction, The GPS vest holds a GPS tracking device that is responsible for tracking heart beat rate,Calorie burning and Energy output.
The information collected by this device from a player is vital to a team doctor and also important in evaluating the performance of an individual player.
